\c 5
\s Rwiyo rwaDhebhora
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhebhora naBharaki mwanakomana waAbhinowami vakaimba nezuva iro vachiti:
\p
\v 2 Kudzai Jehovha, nokuda kwekutsiva kwetsivo dzaIsraeri, kana vanhu vakazvipa nekuzvidira.
\v 3 Inzwai madzimambo, mupe nzeve \add imwi\add* machinda; ini, iyeni, ndichaimbira Jehovha; ndicharumbidza Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri nenziyo.
\v 4 Jehovha, pakubuda kwenyu paSeiri, pakutsika kwenyu muchibva musango reEdhomu, nyika yakadedera, uye matenga akadonha, uye makore akadonha mvura.
\v 5 Makomo akayerera pamberi paJehovha, iro Sinai pamberi paJehovha Mwari waIsraeri.
\v 6 Pamazuva aShamugara, mwanakomana waAnati, pamazuva aJaeri, nzira huru dzakapera, nevafambi vaifamba nenzira dzakakombama.
\v 7 Vene vemisha vakapera kwaIsraeri, vakapera, kusvika ini Dhebhora ndichisimuka, ndichisimuka, \add ini\add* mai kwaIsraeri.
\v 8 Wakasarudza vamwari vatsva; ipapo kukava nehondo pamasuwo. Takaona here nhovo kana pfumo pakati pezvuru makumi mana kwaIsraeri?
\v 9 Moyo wangu uri kuvapi vemurairo vekwaIsraeri, vanozvipa vachizvidira pakati pevanhu; kudzai Jehovha!
\v 10 Vatasvi vemabhiza machena, vagari vemhasa dzinokosha, nevafamba venzira, taurai.
\v 11 Kure namanzwi avanopfura nouta, pavanoteka mvura, ndipo pavacharumbidza mabasa akarurama aJehovha, mabasa akarurama oushe hwake muna Israeri. Ipapo vanhu vaJehovha vakaburukira kumasuwo.
\p
\v 12 Muka, muka, Dhebhora; muka, muka, iwe uimbe rwiyo! Simuka Bharaki, utape vatapwa vako, iwe mwanakomana waAbhinowami.
\v 13 Ipapo vakange vakasara vavakuru navanhu vakaburuka, Jehovha wakaburuka nokuda kwangu kuzorwa navane simba.
\v 14 Kuna Efuremu ndokwakabva vanomudzi wavo paAmareki, vachikutevera iwe Bhenjamini pakati pavanhu vako. PaMakiri ndipo pakaburukira varairi, nokuna Zebhuruni avo vakabata tsvimbo yokukunda.
\v 15 Machinda aIsaskari akange ana Dhebhora; saIsaskari, ndizvo zvakange zvakaitawo Bharaki; vakamhanyira kumupata vachitevera tsoka dzake. Pahova dzaRubheni Pakange pane mirangariro mikuru yomoyo.
\v 16 Wakagarireiko pasi pakati pamatanga ezvipfuwo, uchiteerera kurira kwenyere dzinoridzirwa makwai? Pahova dzaRubheni pakange pano kunzvera kukuru komoyo.
\v 17 Giriyadhi wakagara mhiri kwaJoridhani; newe Dhani, wakagarireiko pazvikepe? Asheri wakagara zvake pamahombekombe egungwa, wakarambira apo panopinda mvura panyika.
\v 18 Zebhuruni ndivanhu vakange vasingatyi kusvikira parufu, naNafutari panzvimbo dzenyika dzakakwirira.
\v 19 Madzimambo akauya akarwa, ipapo madzimambo eKenani akarwawo paTaanaki, pamvura zhinji yeMegidho; havana kuwana fuma yemari.
\v 20 Nyeredzi dzakarwa dziri kudenga, dzakarwa naSisera dziri panzira dzadzo.
\v 21 Rwizi Kishoni rwakavakukura, irwo rwizi rwekare, rwizi Kishoni. Mweya wangu, pfuura nesimba.
\v 22 Nguva iyo makumbo amabhiza akarovera pasi nokumhanya, kuri kumhanya kwavakasimba.
\v 23 Tuka Merozi ndizvo zvinotaura mutumwa waJehovha, tuka zvakaipa avo vageremo. Nokuti havana kuuya kuzobatsira Jehovha, kuzobatsira Jehovha pakurwa kwake navane simba.
\v 24 Pakati pavakadzi Jaeri ngaarumbidzwe, iye mukadzi waHebheri muKeni, ngaarumbidzwe pakati pavakadzi patende.
\v 25 Wakakumbira mvura, iye akamupa mukaka; wakamuvigira mukaka wakafa pandiro yamambo.
\v 26 Wakabata mbambo noruoko rwake, nenyundo yomubati norudyi rwake, akarova Sisera nenyundo, akaboora musoro wake; wakarova, akaboora zvavovo zvake.
\v 27 Wakakotama patsoka dzake, akawa, ipapo paakakotama, ndipo paakawira pasi, afa.
\v 28 Wakatarira pahwindo, akadana, mai vaSisera vakadana pautanda hwaro; ngoro yake inononokereiko kusvika? Makumbo engoro dzake anononokereiko?
\v 29 Vakadzi vake, vakakudzwa, vakachenjera, vakamupindura, naiye amene wakazvipindura, achiti:
\v 30 Havana kuwana here zvavakapamba, havana kuzvigovana here? Zvimwe murume umwe neumwe unopiwa musikana mumwe, kana vasikana vaviri; zvimwe Sisera uchapiwa nguvo dzakapambiwa dzamavara-vara, nguvo dzakapambiwa dzemicheka yakarukwa yamavara-vara, nguvo dzamavara-vara dzakarukwa kunhivi dzese, dzakafanira mitsipa yavakapamba?
\v 31 Saizvozvo vavengi venyu vese ngavaparadzwe, Jehovha; asi ivo vanokudai ngavave sezuva, kana richibuda nesimba raro! Nyika ikazorora makore ana makumi mana.
